00:30:11,830 --> 00:30:14,103
Scott: Like, "Hey, Gnarwals, check this game.

539
00:30:14,304 --> 00:30:15,028
Scott: Why don't you play this

540
00:30:15,068 --> 00:30:15,330
Scott: game?".

541
00:30:15,452 --> 00:30:16,450
Scott: I didn't know anything about it.

