00:30:16,490 --> 00:30:20,890
Scott: Other than that, it was one of those indie, local multiplayer type of games.

543
00:30:20,950 --> 00:30:22,729
Rym: It's Gnarwals plus Nidhogg.

544
00:30:23,982 --> 00:30:24,150
Scott: Yeah.

545
00:30:24,371 --> 00:30:28,290
Scott: Well, now that we played it, we finally got around to playing it at this party.

546
00:30:29,333 --> 00:30:38,470
Rym: So, this game, people kept rotating in and out playing it for hours and hours and hours and hours and hours, yelling and screaming and disrupting the German board games we were trying to play.

547
00:30:38,850 --> 00:30:41,569
Scott: I played it a bit, and it was fun for a bit, but then I was done with it.

