808
00:44:01,791 --> 00:44:03,629
Scott: For example, I have one Schiffbau in my hand.

809
00:44:04,071 --> 00:44:12,410
Scott: Could I say, "I have one Schiffbau or one something I don't have," and then always give the Schiffbau?

810
00:44:12,952 --> 00:44:13,759
Rym: No, you cannot.

811
00:44:13,779 --> 00:44:15,029
Rym: I'm reasonably sure.

