00:44:50,190 --> 00:44:51,730
Scott: Right, you're negotiating without directly negotiating.

821
00:44:51,950 --> 00:45:03,464
Scott: By saying that you want something, someone just said they have one something and it goes around and no one has anything, and then you're like, "I want two of that something you just said you had one

